HEADWORD: Transcursion
<hw>Trans*cur"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. L.
<ets>transcursio</ets> a passing over. See <er>Transcur</er>.]</ety>
<def>A rambling or ramble; a passage over bounds; an excursion.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Howell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
